Global Cattle Gate Market Insights
Cattle Gate Market size was valued at USD 1.20 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.00 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.50% from 2024 to 2030.

Cattle Gate Market Overview
The global cattle gate market is projected to reach a market value of approximately USD 2.5 billion by 2028, growing at a steady CAGR of 5.2% from 2021. This growth is driven by increasing demand for livestock management solutions and advancements in agricultural automation. With the rise of the global population and the expansion of the meat industry, cattle gates are being used more extensively for controlling livestock movement, enhancing operational efficiency, and ensuring better animal welfare in farms across the globe. Technological advancements, along with a growing focus on animal management, are expected to push the market's growth further.

